		{"id":"1e64173efd68d5cb","x":1130,"y":1895,"width":250,"height":245,"type":"text","text":"- [Street](https://www.avamc.se/152-street \"Street\")\n- [Race](https://www.avamc.se/153-race \"Race\")\n- [Adventure](https://www.avamc.se/154-adventure \"Adventure\")\n- [Touring](https://www.avamc.se/155-touring \"Touring\")\n- [Cross](https://www.avamc.se/156-cross \"Cross\")\n- [Junior](https://www.avamc.se/157-junior \"Junior\")\n- [Tillbehör/reservdelar](https://www.avamc.se/202-tillbehor-reservdelar \"Tillbehör/reservdelar\")"},
